text: "You Oughta Know" is a song from Alanis Morissette from her third studio album Jagged Little Pill. It reached the Top 10 in Australia and the United States. The song was released in the United States on July 7, 1995. It received generally positive reviews by critics. ==References== Category:1995 songs Category:Alanis Morissette songs Category:Rock songs
title: You Oughta Know
